  "title": "面壁 MiniCPM-V 4.5 发布：「高刷」多模态",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247504790&idx=1&sn=1d217f1ebabf60e376642aa012bf96eb",
  "date": "2025-08-26 12:08:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"padding:40px 20px;background-size:100px 100px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.02) 2px, transparent 2px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.02) 2px, transparent 2px);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"color: #666;margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">ahhhhhhhhhh~~~</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #666;margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">面壁</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">发了个很有趣的模型&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">MiniCPM-V 4.5</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #666;margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">把视觉模型... 卷到了一个非常别致，但实用的地方</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #666;margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 24px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">高刷</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 40px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-size: 28px;font-weight: bold;color: #333;border-bottom: 3px solid #69D36C;display: inline-block;padding-bottom: 5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">高刷：直观比较</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"color: #666;margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🫲左侧高刷，右侧低刷🫱</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"border-radius:20px;padding:20px;box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);margin:0 auto;max-width:800px;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"427\" data-backw=\"480\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWePGqJD05cm7bqtjibA4pOiatSd06bvTobgAia4Qmu6JbgIRPrNycX64Zg/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"496\" data-cropsely2=\"661\" data-imgfileid=\"100021116\" data-ratio=\"0.8895833333333333\" style=\"display:block;max-width:100%;border-radius:15px;box-sizing:border-box;border:1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);margin-top:0px;margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;width:100%;\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"480\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2600c5a9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWePGqJD05cm7bqtjibA4pOiatSd06bvTobgAia4Qmu6JbgIRPrNycX64Zg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:center;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">猫猫来自...b站up「咪猫胖啊」，猫猫可爱</span></span></b></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #555;line-height: 1.6;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);\">MiniCPM-V 4.5</span>&nbsp;眼中，是左侧</span></b></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);line-height: 1.6;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">10fps，画面流畅，猫猫可爱</span></span></b></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #555;line-height: 1.6;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);\">其他大模型</span>眼中，是右侧</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span></b></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #555;line-height: 1.6;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">1fps，画面跳跃，猫猫可爱</span></span></b></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #555;line-height: 1.6;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">以及...问就是</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span></b></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #555;line-height: 1.6;\"><b><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">1帧能玩，2帧流畅，3帧电竞，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">10帧..绝对是高刷</span></span></b></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"color: #666;margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面...让我更系统的来说说这个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">「高刷」</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">由<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">「首款通用排版 Agent」</span>呈现 （建议电脑看）</span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #666;margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\"><img style=\"display:inline-block;width:20px;vertical-align:middle;background-size:cover;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"20\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0dc35af0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Ft%2Fwx_fed%2Fwe-emoji%2Fres%2Fassets%2Fnewemoji%2FYellowdog.png\"><img style=\"display:inline-block;width:20px;vertical-align:middle;background-size:cover;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"20\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0dc35af0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Ft%2Fwx_fed%2Fwe-emoji%2Fres%2Fassets%2Fnewemoji%2FYellowdog.png\"><img style=\"display:inline-block;width:20px;vertical-align:middle;background-size:cover;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"20\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0dc35af0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Ft%2Fwx_fed%2Fwe-emoji%2Fres%2Fassets%2Fnewemoji%2FYellowdog.png\"></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #666;margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;background-color: #F7F7F7;padding: 40px 20px;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.02) 2px, transparent 2px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.02) 2px, transparent 2px);background-size: 100px 100px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: #666;margin-top: 10px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GitHub：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #666;margin-top: 10px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM-o\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM-o</a></span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:40px 30px;margin:20px auto;max-width:900px;width:100%;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Heiti SC', sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: space-between;min-height: 400px;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 25%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;text-align: left;\">\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 24px;color: #d99c6c;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">MiniCPM-V 4.5</span></p>\n      <p style=\"border-top: 1px solid #d99c6c;width: 80%;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-top: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">面壁 · 开源新旗舰</span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-top: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span></p>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;color: #b0b0b0;\">\n      <p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">8B参数，性能越级超越72B，堪称最强端侧多模态</span></p>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">首个高刷「鹰眼级」模型，看得准、看得快、看得长！</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width: 45%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;\">\n     <div style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:200px;line-height:1;font-family:'KaiTi', 'STKaiti', serif;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\">高</span></p>\n      <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: -20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">刷</span></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.3em;font-size:32px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:40px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">鹰眼视觉</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"width: 20%;writing-mode: vertical-rl;text-orientation: mixed;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: space-between;\">\n     <p style=\"font-size: 16px;color: #d99c6c;letter-spacing: 5px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">30B以下最强多模态</span></p>\n     <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 2.2;color: #b0b0b0;text-align: left;\">\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">单图理解领先GPT-4o</span></p>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">视频理解超越Qwen-VL</span></p>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">文档解析同级最佳</span></p>\n      <p><span leaf=\"\">端侧友好极致能效</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"border-top: 2px solid #d99c6c;margin-top: 40px;padding-top: 30px;text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:30px;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型亮点一览</span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 25px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;\">\n     <p style=\"color: #d99c6c;font-weight: bold;margin-right: 20px;font-size: 16px;flex-shrink: 0;width: 120px;\"><span leaf=\"\">首个高刷模型</span></p>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">首个「高刷视频理解」多模态模型，兼顾性能与效率</span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">同等视觉token开销下，可接收6倍视频帧数，达到96倍视觉压缩率，是同类模型的12-24倍</span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在MotionBench、FavorBench榜单中达到同尺寸SOTA，超越Qwen2.5-VL 72B</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 25px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;\">\n     <p style=\"color: #d99c6c;font-weight: bold;margin-right: 20px;font-size: 16px;flex-shrink: 0;width: 120px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最强多模态</span></p>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">30B以下最强多模态，多项能力越级领先</span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">图片理解（OpenCompass）领先GPT-4o、Gemini-2.0-Pro等闭源模型；长视频、OCR、文档解析等能力均达到同级SOTA，并超越Qwen2.5-VL 72B</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 25px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;\">\n     <p style=\"color: #d99c6c;font-weight: bold;margin-right: 20px;font-size: 16px;flex-shrink: 0;width: 120px;\"><span leaf=\"\">端侧友好</span></p>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">极致推理性价比，最佳推理效率</span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">显存占用、平均推理时间等优势显著，采用3帧打包策略推理，时间开销（未计抽帧）仅为同级模型的1/10</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 25px;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;\">\n     <p style=\"color: #d99c6c;font-weight: bold;margin-right: 20px;font-size: 16px;flex-shrink: 0;width: 120px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可控推理</span></p>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持长思考、短思考可控混合推理</span></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">常规模式提供出色多模态理解能力，深度思考模式专注复杂与复合型推理任务，实现性能与响应速度的有效平衡</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"border-top: 1px solid #555;margin-top: 40px;padding-top: 30px;text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从“看PPT”到“理解动态画面”</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">此前，主流多模态模型通常采取 1fps 抽帧，缺失了绝大部分视觉信息。MiniCPM-V 4.5 将<span textstyle=\"\">视觉能力从 1fps 升级到 10fps</span>，通过显著增加抽帧频次，瞬间捕捉，洞见细节，面对一闪而过的画面，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">比顶尖云端模型，如 GPT/Gemini，看得更准、更细</span>。</span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-top: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在体现高刷视频理解能力的 MotionBench、FavorBench 两项榜单中，MiniCPM-V 4.5 达到同尺寸 SOTA，且超过 Qwen2.5-VL 72B，实现越级领先</span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021112\" alt=\"MotionBench and FavorBench Results\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display:block;max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:20px auto;width:100%;\" data-backw=\"518\" data-backh=\"691\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=03d181e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWaibYQjFhHchsshoXDWLtMK5F8GdZIcR0z1uGxiaBZ8t0ibGJqjE6kbwJw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"border-top: 1px solid #555;margin-top: 40px;padding-top: 30px;text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:30px;\"><span leaf=\"\">全能多模态SOTA表现</span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">图片理解性能</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 OpenCompass 测评中，领先 GPT-4o、GPT-4.1、Gemini-2.0-Pro 等众多闭源模型 ，甚至超过 Qwen2.5-VL 72B，实现越级领先</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100021140\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3571428571428572\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1792\" style=\"display:block;max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:20px auto;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWW5ibegNM1GRDtbP0Y1oggno2ricIPjATGL3x2wWSBbSCTYYHib5Woibspg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"518\" data-cropsely2=\"691\" data-backw=\"518\" data-backh=\"703\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a274bd1d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWW5ibegNM1GRDtbP0Y1oggno2ricIPjATGL3x2wWSBbSCTYYHib5Woibspg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;margin-top: 30px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频理解性能</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 LVBench、MLVU、Video-MME 等榜单中，均达到同级最佳水平</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"691\" data-backw=\"518\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWqEQfZVKmRF9OGVSvTiaqh7CRV3O5Kl3gHINdy8omLGbV8ehsLnq2nOA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"518\" data-cropsely2=\"691\" data-imgfileid=\"100021141\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"display:block;max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:20px auto;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1920\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7523af2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWqEQfZVKmRF9OGVSvTiaqh7CRV3O5Kl3gHINdy8omLGbV8ehsLnq2nOA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;margin-top: 30px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">复杂文档识别</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 OmniDocBench 榜单的 OverallEdit、TextEdit、TableEdit 三项指标上，均取得了通用多模态模型同级别的 SOTA 表现</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"OmniDocBench Benchmark\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"691\" data-backw=\"518\" data-imgfileid=\"100021108\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" style=\"display:block;max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:20px auto;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c87b1133&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWLB4LBWC4eazicS95Vj7ydouk4EXhaQD5qcJqicfr1HxsbE5czGsnc1Ew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;margin-top: 30px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">极致推理性价比</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在覆盖短、中、长三种类型的视频理解评测集 Video-MME 上，MiniCPM-V 4.5 采用 3 帧打包策略进行推理，时间开销（未计算模型抽帧时间）仅为同级模型的 1/10&nbsp;</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"703\" data-backw=\"518\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWwG61ABXupud4gFiaXAsqjX0c4RUqt3h44sX9iax7a3X6YeK6eKsWib91g/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"518\" data-cropsely2=\"691\" data-imgfileid=\"100021123\" data-ratio=\"1.3571428571428572\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"display:block;max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:20px auto;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1792\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aedf1c48&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYp7CCicTYcfKicicazMvJmwjIWwG61ABXupud4gFiaXAsqjX0c4RUqt3h44sX9iax7a3X6YeK6eKsWib91g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"border-top: 1px solid #555;margin-top: 40px;padding-top: 30px;text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:30px;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心技术解析</span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3D-Resampler：高密度视频压缩</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;line-height: 1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\">为解决性能和效率的权衡，MiniCPM-V 4.5 将模型结构从 2D-Resampler 拓展为 3D-Resampler。视频按每N帧分组，3D-Resampler 对每个视频组进行高密度压缩编码，得到固定数量的视觉token。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">在推理开销不变的情况下，实现最大10fps的高刷</span>视频理解能力</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;margin-top: 30px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">统一OCR与知识推理学习</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;line-height: 1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过连续控制图像中「文字信息可见度」（即对文字框区域施加不同程度的噪音），<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">首次实现 OCR 和知识学习两种范式的有效融合</span>。模型可根据噪音程度，在OCR、知识学习、混合能力学习之间无缝切换，低成本实现领先的 OCR 和多模态知识能力</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;margin-top: 30px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通用域混合推理强化学习</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #b0b0b0;line-height: 1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\">提出混合推理的强化学习方案，在训练中同时激活常规和深度思考模式，实现在相同训练时长下，常规模式性能显著增强，深度思考模式性能保持。最终通过轻量化的 RLAIF-V 训练，模型在保持推理能力的同时显著降低了幻觉</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"border-top: 2px solid #d99c6c;margin-top: 50px;padding-top: 30px;text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:25px;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源社区传送门</span></p>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 2.5;color: #b0b0b0;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Github</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM-o\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM-o</a></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Hugging Face</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/openbmb/MiniCPM-V-4_5\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/openbmb/MiniCPM-V-4_5</a></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">ModelScope</span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.modelscope.cn/models/OpenBMB/MiniCPM-V-4_5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.modelscope.cn/models/OpenBMB/MiniCPM-V-4_5</a></span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span></p>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">以及...更多的场景演示</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "面壁智能发布 MiniCPM-V 4.5，首次实现 10fps“高刷”视频理解，以 8B 参数超越 72B 模型，并在多模态任务上达到 SOTA，同时兼顾端侧高效推理。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "面壁智能发布 MiniCPM-V 4.5，首次实现 10fps“高刷”视频理解，以 8B 参数超越 72B 模型，并在多模态任务上达到 SOTA，同时兼顾端侧高效推理。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了面壁智能最新发布的 MiniCPM-V 4.5 多模态大模型。该模型以 8B 参数量，在多项基准测试中超越了 72B 参数的同类模型，实现了越级性能。其核心亮点是首次引入了“高刷”视频理解能力，将传统多模态模型 1fps 的抽帧频率提升至 10fps，通过 3D-Resampler 技术在同等视觉 token 开销下接收 6 倍视频帧数，达到 96 倍视觉压缩率，显著提升了模型对动态细节的捕捉能力。MiniCPM-V 4.5 在图片理解（如 OpenCompass 榜单领先 GPT-4o）、长视频理解（如 LVBench、MLVU、Video-MME 榜单同级最佳）、OCR 和复杂文档解析（如 OmniDocBench 榜单 SOTA）等任务上均达到同级 SOTA 水平。此外，模型还具备端侧友好特性，通过 3 帧打包策略显著降低了推理时间和显存占用，使其推理时间开销仅为同级模型的 1/10，并支持长短思考可控混合推理。文章还简要阐述了 3D-Resampler、统一 OCR 与知识推理学习、通用域混合推理强化学习等核心技术，并提供了开源社区链接。",
